<li><a href="/brenzan-s-art-dump">BrenZan's Art Dump</a> - &quot;Bumaro (or any other mekhanite priest)&quot;, &quot;scp 076-2&quot;, and &quot;how to contain scp 076-2&quot; | <a href="https://thelivingtrashcan.tumblr.com/">Artist's Tumblr</a></li>
<li><a href="/hawks-n-artworks">Hawks n Artworks</a> - Brand new artwork page with works in a few different styles. Be sure to check out the atmospheric Polaroids in the Personal Art section.</li>
